N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 50.6 - Owner disinfecting nonquarantined premises

State Regulations

Nothing herein contained will prohibit a owner of other
premises not under quarantine from disinfecting his own premises, buildings, railway cars, boats or other objects, unless otherwise directed by the
commissioner. Notes
